quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  13,38,"Kandi rwose twohereje Intumwa mbere yawe (yewe Muhamadi), tunazigenera (gushaka) abagore (no kugira) urubyaro. Ndetse nta Ntumwa yazana igitangaza bidaturutse ku bushake bwa Allah. Buri kintu cyose gifite igihe cyagenewe"
  13,39,"Allah ahanagura cyangwa akemeza ibyo ashaka (mu mategeko ye). Kandi ni We ufite igitabo gihatse ibindi [(Al Lawuh-ul Mahfudh (urubaho rurinzwe]"
  13,40,"N’iyo twakwereka (yewe Muhamadi) bimwe mu byo tubasezeranya (ibihano) cyangwa tukakuzuriza igihe cyawe (ugapfa), mu by’ukuri inshingano zawe ni ugusohoza ubutumwa, maze ibarura rikaba iryacu"
  13,41,"Ese ntibabona ko mu by’ukuri dusenya ubutaka tukagenda tubugabanya mu mpande zabwo zose? Allah ni We utegeka kandi nta wavuguruza itegeko rye, ndetse ni We ubanguka mu ibarura"
  13,42,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi babayeho mbere yabo bacuriye imigambi mibisha (Intumwa zabo), ariko Allah ni We uburizamo imigambi mibisha yose. Azi neza ibyo buri muntu akora, kandi abahakanyi bazamenya uzagira iherezo ryiza"
  13,43,Ba bandi bahakanye baravuga bati “Ntabwo (wowe Muhamadi) uri Intumwa.” Vuga uti “Allah arahagije kuba umuhamya hagati yanjye namwe ndetse n’abafite ubumenyi bw’igitabo (baje kuyoboka Isilamu).”